(4, 37, 0, 'Thank you, dear poets,\r\nFor sharing your wisdom, your love,\r\nYour understanding, your compassion,\r\nYour language, your culture, your beliefs,\r\nYour pristine feelings collected from the depth\r\nOf your hearts. I''ve been enormously enriched by you all.......EXACTLY MY POE FRIEND! ', '2014-05-26 06:47:52'),
(5, 37, 0, 'Poet Khairul Ahsan\r\nOne of the talented and gifted poet.\r\nIts one of the blessings you have.\r\nHis poems are very pleasant to read.\r\nHis poems flows freely on any topics.\r\nHe recognise other readers poems with praise.\r\nMay you keep on contributing valuable poems to this poetic world.\r\nWishing you all the best.\r\nGod Bless You! ', '2014-05-26 06:48:12'),
(6, 37, 0, 'I enjoyed reading Khairul''s biography. He took the time to write extensively, and to share private things about himself, bringing his personality vividly to life. I could feel the quietness and humility in his sentences, and his appreciation of his friendships with people everywhere. His poetry is very much enjoyed here at PH, and I am pleased to know him. ', '2014-05-26 06:48:34'),
